RMK_TEXT: AIRCRAFT HELICOPTER BELL 407, HELICOPTER FLIGHT HAD ARRIVED AT WEST DELTA 106 PLATFORM (WD106) AT 0819 (LOCAL) WITH FOUR PASSENGERS ON BOARD. THE FOUR PASSENGERS WERE DROPPED OFF AND THREE PASSENGERS BOARDED THE AIRCRAFT. THE ROTORCRAFT DEPARTED WD106 ENROUTE TO GALLIANO, LA (GAO) AND CRASHED BACK ONTO THE HELIDECK DURING TAKEOFF, SUBSEQUENTLY BREAKING APART AND FELL INTO THE GULF OF MEXICO.
